                  <summary>I) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 3ra-43rb)&#xD; - Bǝsrāta Mātewos “Gospel of
                     Matthew” (fols. 3ra-43rb)&#xD; - Short postscript (fol. 43rb)&#xD; II) Gospel
                     of Mark (fols. 44ra-66vb)&#xD; - Bǝsrāta Mārqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols.
                     44ra-66vb)&#xD; III) Gospel of Luke (fols. 68ra-110rb)&#xD; - Bǝsrāta Luqās
                     “Gospel of Luke” (fols. 68ra-110rb)&#xD; - Postscript (fol. 110rb)&#xD; IV)
                     Gospel of John (fols. 110va-143ra)&#xD; - Biography of John (fol.
                     110va-vb)&#xD; - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 20 titles (fol.
                     110vb)&#xD; - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols. 111ra-142vb)&#xD; -
                     Postscript (fol. 143ra)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-8.</summary>
